{
  "name": "Medical Release Grim Weapon",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Medical.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You weave summoning seals together, infusing them into your weapon and medical release chakra that manifests as an echo of reaping black chakra enhances the weapon you touch. You cannot lose concentration of this jutsu as a result of damage.</p><p>For the duration, the weapon you affected by this jutsu is enhanced by the reaper's black necrotic chakra. Enhanced weapons deal an additional 1d6 Necrotic damage twice per turn. If the affected creature has regained hit points prior in this initiative roll, this damage is increased to 1d12.</p><p>Once per round, creatures who take necrotic damage from this enhanced weapon reduces the number of hit points they regain by half.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank or higher, increase the damage this jutsu deals by 1d6 or 1d12 respectively. If this jutsu is cast at S-Rank, creatures who take necrotic damage from this enhanced weapon cannot regain hit points for the duration of this jutsu.</p>",
